                           Hebrew letters in Ps. 118 (e.g., fols. 30rb, 31va, 33rb); abbreviations;
                           elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals; some
                           other words, e.g., halle luya (e.g., fols. 9vb, 10ra), ṣällǝyu (e.g.,
                           fols. 16ra, 24vb), wa-yǝbälu ḥǝzb (e.g., fols. 17vb, 18ra), kǝśtat (e.g.,
